User case: Game over

Summary: when the player is destroyed move to the game over screen

Priority: low

Normal flow 1: the player is destroyed
	User action		|		System action
	
1.1							display "Game Over"

1.2							show highScore screen and let
							the player type a name if his/her
							score is in the top 10	

1.3	clicks "main menu"
	button

1.4							shows main menu				